I tried it with Github myself now and got it working with the following config in the `settings.py`:

```
SOCIALACCOUNT_PROVIDERS = {
    "github": {
        "APPS": [
            {
                "provider_id": "github",
                "name": "Github",
                "client_id": "XXXXXX",
                "secret": "XXXXXX",
                }
            ]
    },
}
```
`provider_id` and `name` can be freely chosen. Additionally `allauth.socialaccount.providers.github` needs to be added to the installed apps.

